  "title": "Warehouse Admin / Warehouse Clerk #75732",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturer (Commercial Cleaning Equipment)</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Warehouse Admin / Warehouse Clerk</strong></li><li>Working Location: Gul Crescent (Transport provided at Boon Lay, Lakeside, Chinese Garden, Yew Tee)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Monday-Friday, 8:15AM-5:30PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to $2700 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Provide daily administrative support for store operations (Spare parts department), including preparing local purchase orders.</li><li>Receive and process transfer orders and goods received and generate pick lists.</li><li>Support inventory control activities, including stock checks and stock adjustments.</li><li>Keep the Warehouse Management System (WMS) updated accurately and on time.</li><li>Handle phone calls and respond to inquiries from internal teams.</li><li>Prepare and update documents such as letters, reports, and emails.</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties which may be assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum GCE “O” Level, with at least 1 year of relevant work experience.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office (e.g., Word, Excel, PowerPoint).</li><li>Experience with Microsoft Dynamic 365 will be advantageous.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#75732 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
